TITLE: Configuring to Ignore Files Without Code
DESCRIPTION: ESLint configuration to ignore files that do not contain code when applying the JSX filename extension rule.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-react/blob/master/docs/rules/jsx-filename-extension.md#2025-04-14_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
"rules": {
  "react/jsx-filename-extension": [1, { "ignoreFilesWithoutCode": true }]
}
```

