TITLE: Rule Configuration Format
DESCRIPTION: ESLint configuration format for the require-optimization rule showing enabled state and decorator options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-react/blob/master/docs/rules/require-optimization.md#2025-04-14_snippet_2

