TITLE: Configuring the 'forbid-foreign-prop-types' rule in ESLint
DESCRIPTION: Configuration example showing how to enable the rule with its options in an ESLint configuration file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-react/blob/master/docs/rules/forbid-foreign-prop-types.md#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
...
"react/forbid-foreign-prop-types": [<enabled>, { "allowInPropTypes": [<boolean>] }]
...
```

